{"id":135027,"name":"Remove The Shadow Gradient on YouTube Video Player","description":"Removes the shadow gradient behind the YouTube video player bar and gradient above. Helps a little bit with reading and seeing stuff normally hidden by this bar. :P I miss the old player that didn't cover videos :'/\r\nI've made the option to set the opacity between 0% and 100% to vary how visible the gradients are. hope you enjoy~ ^_^\r\nI'll try find out if I can give the option to color them, I'm still learning. let me know in the comments if you want this feature, cheers. :D\r\n\r\n-If you want the Player bar to be moved below the video, try my other style for it: style 137651","user":{"id":364903,"name":"Joseph Dickson","email":"josephgdickson@gmail.com","paypal_email":"josephgdickson@gmail.com","homepage":null,"about":"I'm a lousy coder, total novice! but I've learned only basically how to hide elements through being annoyed by them. :3","license":"ccby"},"updated":"2016-12-01T04:21:50.000Z","weekly_install_count":39,"total_install_count":6587,"rating":5.0,"after_screenshot_name":"https://userstyles.org/style_screenshots/135027_after.jpeg?r=1687593692","obsoleting_style_id":null,"obsoleting_style_name":null,"obsolete":0,"admin_delete_reason_id":null,"obsoletion_message":null,"screenshots":null,"license":"publicdomain","created":"2016-11-11T07:51:19.000Z","category":"site","raw_subcategory":"youtube","subcategory":"youtube","additional_info":"Made: 11-November-2016\r\nOpacity Update: 01-December-2016","style_tags":[],"css":"@-moz-document url-prefix(\"https://www.youtube.com/\") {\r\n/* Remove Shadow on YouTube Video Player Bar*/\r\n#movie_player \u003e div.ytp-gradient-bottom {opacity: /*[[GBOTTOM]]*/ !important;}\r\n#movie_player \u003e div.ytp-gradient-top {opacity: /*[[GTOP]]*/ !important;}\r\n/*set opacity between 0 and 1 to set how visible the gradients are*/\r\n}","discussions":[{"id":52821,"name":"An option for a fully opaque background?","rating":3,"created":"2016-1